flowchart TD
    START([main.go starts]) --> FLAGS[Parse flags<br/>--transport, --addr, --healthcheck, --version]
    FLAGS --> VERSION{--version?}
    VERSION -->|Yes| PRINT_VER[Print version, exit 0]
    VERSION -->|No| HEALTH{--healthcheck?}
    HEALTH -->|Yes| HTTP_GET[GET /healthz with 5s timeout<br/>Exit 0 on 200, exit 1 otherwise]
    HEALTH -->|No| LOAD[config.Load<br/>Read all env vars, validate]
    LOAD --> VALIDATE[gemini.ValidateRegistryAtStartup<br/>Check for sentinel model IDs]
    VALIDATE --> SENTINEL{Sentinel IDs<br/>present?}
    SENTINEL -->|Yes| FAIL_SENTINEL[Exit: unverified model IDs]
    SENTINEL -->|No| SECRETS[security.RegisterSecret<br/>API key + auth token]
    SECRETS --> LOGGER[Create structured logger]
    LOGGER --> CLIENT[gemini.NewClient<br/>SDK init + pro semaphore<br/>optional if per-user keys only]
    CLIENT --> CACHE[gemini.NewClientCache<br/>per-user client pool]
    CACHE --> MCP_SRV[server.NewMCPServer<br/>Register 4 tools]
    MCP_SRV --> OAUTH_BUILD[Build OAuth providers<br/>Google / GitHub]
    OAUTH_BUILD --> OAUTH_STORE[Create OAuth store<br/>+ cleanup goroutine]
    OAUTH_STORE --> TRANSPORT{--transport?}
    TRANSPORT -->|stdio| STDIO[server.ServeStdio<br/>Block until stdin closes]
    TRANSPORT -->|http| TLS{TLS configured?}
    TLS -->|Yes| HTTPS[http.Server.ListenAndServeTLS<br/>Graceful shutdown on SIGTERM/SIGINT]
    TLS -->|No| HTTP_SRV[http.Server.ListenAndServe<br/>Graceful shutdown on SIGTERM/SIGINT]
